            <li>‚Ä¢ Belongings between moves</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Seasonal items (garden furniture, decorations)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Inherited items you're not ready to sort</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Downsizing overflow</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üíº</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Business Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Cost-effective space for commercial needs.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Stock and inventory</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Office equipment and furniture</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Archived documents and records</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Tools and trade equipment</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ E-commerce fulfilment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üéì</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Student Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Flexible options for university students.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Summer vacation storage</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Year abroad storage</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Moving between accommodation</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Affordable small units</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Collection and delivery options</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Security Features -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Security You Can Trust</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üìπ</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">24/7 CCTV</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Round-the-clock video monitoring of all areas</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üö®</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Individual Alarms</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Each unit has its own alarm system</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üîê</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Secure Access</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">PIN codes and controlled entry points</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Insurance Options</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Contents insurance available for peace of mind</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Unit Sizes -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Choosing the Right Unit Size</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Storage units come in various sizes to match your needs. Here's a guide to help you choose:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 text-primary font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded inline-block mb-4">15-25 sq ft</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Locker / Small</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Like a large wardrobe</p>
          <ul class="text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Documents and files</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Small furniture items</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Sports equipment</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Seasonal clothing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 text-primary font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded inline-block mb-4">35-50 sq ft</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Garden Shed Size</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Contents of a small flat</p>
          <ul class="text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Studio flat contents</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Garden furniture</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Bikes and equipment</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Small office items</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 text-primary font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded inline-block mb-4">75-100 sq ft</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Single Garage Size</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Contents of 1-2 bed flat</p>
          <ul class="text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Flat contents</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Sofa and furniture</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Multiple appliances</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Business stock</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 text-primary font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded inline-block mb-4">150+ sq ft</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Double Garage+</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Contents of 3+ bed house</p>
          <ul class="text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Full house contents</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Vehicles/boats</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Large business stock</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Workshop space</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Flexible Terms -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Flexible Storage Terms</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
        <p class="mb-6">
          Self storage adapts to your timeline. Most facilities offer contracts from as little as one week, with the flexibility to extend as needed. There are typically no long-term commitments required, and you can often upgrade or downgrade your unit size as your storage needs change.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1 Week+</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Minimum rental periods</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">No Deposit</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">At many facilities</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">24/7 Access</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Available at select sites</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          Access hours vary by facility ‚Äî many offer extended hours or even 24/7 access for customers who need to retrieve items outside normal business hours. When comparing options, check whether access times suit your schedule.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Store -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What Can You Store?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-600 mb-4">‚úì Commonly Stored Items</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Furniture (sofas, beds, tables, chairs)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Household appliances</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Clothing and personal effects</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Books, DVDs, vinyl records</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Sports and hobby equipment</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Garden furniture and tools</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Business stock and inventory</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Office furniture and equipment</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Archived documents</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Seasonal decorations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-600 mb-4">‚úó Not Permitted</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Perishable food items</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Hazardous materials</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Flammable substances</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Illegal items</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Living things (plants, animals)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Firearms and ammunition</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Chemicals and solvents</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Unregistered vehicles</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Check with your storage provider for full terms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Storage Tips -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Storage Tips</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Use uniform boxes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Same-sized boxes stack better and make efficient use of space.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Label everything</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Clear labels on all sides help you find items without unstacking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Create an aisle</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Leave space to walk into the unit for easier access to items at the back.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Protect soft furnishings</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cover sofas and mattresses with dust sheets or storage bags.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Disassemble furniture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Take apart beds and tables to save space and prevent damage.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Keep inventory</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Maintain a list of what's stored ‚Äî useful for insurance and retrieval.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-primary p-8 rounded-r-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Looking for Storage in Bristol?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <a href="https://painlessremovals.co.uk" rel="nofollow" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">Painless Removals</a> can help you find the right storage solution for your needs. Whether you need short-term storage during a move or long-term space for business inventory, they'll match you with secure, affordable options.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="tel:01172870082" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Call 01172 870 082
          </a>
          <a href="#callback-form" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-secondary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
            Request Callback
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CallbackForm />
</BaseLayout>
